Type of Contenct Projection
1. Single
2. Multi
3. Conditional

1. ##Single Contenct Projection
    In Parent component, if we want to send any template then we can write that element inside child selector and access the element in child using ng-content
    example: <child-component><h1>These are latest products</h1></child-component>
            In child Component.html, we can access this using ng-content
2. #Multi Content Projection
    By using selector we can access multi contents
     example: <child-component>
                    <h1>These are latest products</h1>
                    <p structures>With 50% Discounts</p>
              </child-component>
            In child Component.html, we can access this using ng-content
                <ng-content></ng-content>
                <ng-content select ="structures"></ng-content>
